.footer-wrap .nlbox .nlbox-box .subscribe-btn{display:block;height:40px;line-height:40px;border-radius:0 4px 4px 0}
.footer-wrap .nlbox .nlbox-box .gift-cart{color:#666}
.footer-wrap .nlbox .nlbox-box .follow-us-box{margin-top:10px}
.footer-wrap .nlbox .nlbox-box .follow-us-box h3{font-size:14px}
.footer-wrap .nlbox .nlbox-box .follow-us-box .follow-us-list{*zoom:1}
.footer-wrap .nlbox .nlbox-box .follow-us-box .follow-us-list:after{display:block;clear:both;height:0;visibility:hidden;content:'\20'}
.footer-wrap .nlbox .nlbox-box .follow-us-box .follow-us-list li{float:left;margin-left:10px;margin-top:10px}
.footer-wrap .nlbox .nlbox-box .follow-us-box .follow-us-list li a.icn{display:block;background:url(../img/follow.png) no-repeat;width:32px;height:32px}
.footer-wrap .nlbox .nlbox-box .follow-us-box .follow-us-list li a.icn.fb{background-position:0 0}
.footer-wrap .nlbox .nlbox-box .follow-us-box .follow-us-list li a.icn.tw{background-position:-76px 0}
.footer-wrap .nlbox .nlbox-box .follow-us-box .follow-us-list li a.icn.tb{background-position:-114px 0}
.footer-wrap .nlbox .nlbox-box .follow-us-box .follow-us-list li a.icn.g{background-position:-190px 0}
.footer-wrap .nlbox .nlbox-box .follow-us-box .follow-us-list li a.icn.rd{background-position:-266px 0}
.footer-wrap .nlbox .nlbox-box .follow-us-box .follow-us-list li a.icn.b{background-position:-38px 0}
.footer-wrap .nlbox .nlbox-box .follow-us-box .follow-us-list li a.icn.vk{background-position:-228px 0}
.footer-wrap .nlbox .nlbox-box .follow-us-box .follow-us-list li a.icn.db{background-position:-152px 0}
.footer-wrap .payment-method{width:1200px;padding-top:6px;margin:0 auto 6px;text-align:center;font-size:0}
.footer-wrap .payment-method li{height:36px;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;margin:10px 0 10px 2px}
.footer-wrap .payment-method li a{display:block}
.error-wrap{padding:60px 668px 80px 40px;background-color:#f8f5ec}
.error-wrap.error404{background-image:url(../img/mascot404.jpg);background-position:right center;background-repeat:no-repeat}
.error-wrap.error500{background-image:url(../img/mascot500.jpg);background-position:right center;background-repeat:no-repeat}
.error-wrap .error-btn{border:2px solid #e62e04;border-radius:30px;color:#e62e04;font-size:36px;font-weight:700;padding:10px 20px}
.error-wrap .not-found{font-size:26px;margin-top:50px}
.error-wrap p{line-height:25px}
.video{cursor:pointer}
.go-back-top{text-align:center;width:40px;height:40px;line-height:40px;border-radius:40px;background:rgba(51,51,51,.5);position:fixed;bottom:100px;left:50%;margin-left:650px;color:#fff;cursor:pointer}
.go-back-top:hover{background:#333}
.goog-te-gadget{width:1200px;margin:0 auto;text-align:right}
.goog-te-gadget&gt;div{display:inline-black;margin-right:10px}
.brower-list{*zoom:1;margin-left:10px;margin-top:20px}
.brower-list:after{display:block;clear:both;height:0;visibility:hidden;content:'\20'}
.brower-list li{float:left;text-align:center;padding:10px;width:110px;margin-left:10px;border:1px solid #e9e9e9}
.brower-list li:hover{border-color:#ccc}
.brower-list li a:hover{text-decoration:none}
.linkage-select-country{text-align:left;border:1px solid #e9e9e9;position:relative;height:28px;line-height:28px;font-size:12px;background:#fff;cursor:pointer}
.linkage-select-country a.cor i{position:absolute;width:13px;height:28px;top:0;right:10px;background:url(../img/icon.png) no-repeat;background-position:-3px -17px}
.linkage-select-country a.cor:hover{text-decoration:none}
.linkage-select-country.hovered a.cor i{background-position:-3px -38px}
.linkage-select-country .country-list-panel{position:absolute;top:30px;left:0;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e9e9e9;display:block;z-index:99;height:250px;overflow-y:scroll}
.linkage-select-country .country-list-panel li{display:block;width:100%;margin-bottom:0;padding:5px 10px;line-height:15px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow:hidden;font-size:12px;cursor:pointer}
.linkage-select-country .country-list-panel li:hover{background:#e9e9e9}
.linkage-select-country .country-list-panel li.curr{color:#e62e04}
.linkage-select-country .country-list-panel li.linkage-search{cursor:default}
.linkage-select-country .country-list-panel li.linkage-search:hover{background:#fff}
.linkage-select-country .country-list-panel li.linkage-search input{width:90%;background:url(../img/icon.png) no-repeat;background-position:4px 4px;padding-left:25px;height:27px;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box}
.linkage-select-country .country-list-panel li.hot-country{border-bottom:1px solid #ccc;padding-bottom:10px;margin-bottom:10px}
.go-mobile{*zoom:1;height:60px;line-height:60px;border-radius:30px;position:fixed;bottom:150px;right:10px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.3);padding:0 15px;color:#fff;z-index:999;cursor:pointer;font-size:1.4rem}
.go-mobile:after{display:block;clear:both;height:0;visibility:hidden;content:'\20'}
.go-mobile:hover{color:#fff;text-decoration:none}
.go-mobile&gt;span{text-align:center}
.go-mobile .iconfont{display:block;margin-top:-2px;transform:rotate(180deg);margin-left:5px;font-weight:700;font-size:1.4rem;float:left;text-align:center}


.a-href-dialog{
    height:30px;
}
